caption: Records nested 2-3 levels deep
tags: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/recipes
title: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/recipes/nested-records
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Use multiple `[*]`s in the records path; use `..` in bindings to reach the
ancestors.  See the ''Example Trip Itinerary'' profile, which exercises
3-deep nesting (trip → days → activities) with `../date` and
`../../trip-name`.
